### b. **Choose Cloud Migration Strategy**

âœ” 7Râ€™s Model â€” fully correct.

Letâ€™s simplify for better clarity:

| Strategy | Explanation | Example |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Rehost (Lift & Shift)** | Move as-is | VMs â†’ EC2 |
| **Replatform (Lift-tinker-shift)** | Minor adjustments | App server â†’ ECS/EKS, DB â†’ RDS |
| **Refactor (Re-architect)** | Full app redesign | Monolith â†’ Microservices |
| **Repurchase** | Replace with SaaS | On-prem CRM â†’ Salesforce |
| **Relocate** | Move same infra to cloud-native service | On-prem K8s â†’ EKS |
| **Retire** | Decommission unused | Legacy report servers |
| **Retain** | Keep on-prem (hybrid) | Banking, payments on-prem for compliance |

